headline: Payroll Stocks to Watch as June's Jobs Report Comes in Strong
summary: Payroll stocks stood out Thursday as June's Jobs Report came in stronger than expected, marking the 11th consecutive month that the U.S. has exceeded expectations for positive job creation.
